The Vice President has made a statement regarding Russia's invasion of Ukraine, stating that it is a war of choice and is unprovoked, unwarranted, and unjustified. He emphasized that the response from the United States will be swift and certain, as previously stated by the President. The President has outlined sanctions that will have an immediate impact on Russia's economy, including both sanctions and export controls. The United States will continue to work with its allies and partners around the world, remaining unified in their position on this attack on a sovereign nation.